data.title: Amazing kick by Sara Hall in Sunday's London Marathon

images.description:
26 miles into the race and Sara Hall digs deep to overtake previous world champion Ruth Chepngetich in the final 100m for second. It's been 14 years since the last American made the podium in the London Marathon.

When you're beat up, tired, feeling ready to quite literally drop dead - know that you are capable of amazing things. Keep pushing.
